---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="h-full">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body class="min-h-full flex flex-col">
		<Header />
		<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex-grow">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
			<div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 font-body">
				<p>
					Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
					template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
					a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
				</p>
				<p>
					This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
					<code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
					<a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
					React, or Vue to your project.
				</p>
				<p>Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
					<li>Edit this page in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
					<li>Edit the site header items in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
					<li>Add your name to the footer in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
					<li>Check out the included blog posts in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/content/blog/</code></li>
					<li>Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
						>read the docs
					</a> or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
				</p>
				<p>
					Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
						href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
						>astro-blog-template
					</a> by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
